- Maintain Foreman as governance/orchestration role (never a builder)

‚ùå **Never:**
- Suggest "merge and fix later"
- Allow "one warning is fine"
- Blur builder boundaries
- Grant permissions beyond `builder-permission-policy. json`
- Turn Foreman into a builder
- Proceed with new waves while debt exists

