### Phase 1: Framework (This PR) ‚úÖ
- Establish minimal format and canonical quickstart
- Create templates and migration guide
- Migrate one example (governance-repo-administrator)
- Enable new agents to use format immediately

### Phase 2: Systematic Migration (Wave 2+) ‚è≥
- Migrate office-app contracts (FM + builders)
- Refactor test removal sections as canonical references
- Validate approach at scale
- **Explicitly deferred** per migration guide

**Hybrid State is Intentional**:
- Old contracts:  Valid until Wave 2
- New contracts: Use minimal format
- No forced disruption during active campaigns
- Migration guide provides clear path

