- Aligns with AGENT_RECRUITMENT.md
- Aligns with . agent.schema.md
- No contradictions with canonical governance
- Maintains all constitutional requirements via references

### CI Enforcement ‚úÖ
- Size limits prevent bloat (300-line max)
- Forbidden patterns catch duplication
- Governance bindings ensure canonical reference
- **Applies to governance repo . agent files only** (office-app migration in Wave 2)

