## CS2 Override Justification

**Why This Bypasses ZWZDI Blocking Policy**:

1. **Pre-authorized** before ZWZDI campaign launch
2. **Infrastructure repair**, not new feature work
3. **Operational necessity**: Agent recruitment currently blocked
