Example from UI Builder (130 lines total):

```markdown
## One-Time Build | Zero Test Debt | Immediate Remedy

**Authority**:  BUILD_PHILOSOPHY.md, zero-test-debt-constitutional-rule.md

**Pre-Build**:  Arch frozen, QA-to-Red RED | **Prohibited**: Start before frozen, trial-and-error  
**Zero Debt**: No .skip(), .todo(), partial (99%=FAILURE) | **Response**: STOP, FIX, RE-RUN, VERIFY 100%  
**Prior Debt Discovery**:  STOP, DOCUMENT, ESCALATE to FM, BLOCKED, WAIT
```

**Reduction**: 83% while preserving all content.   
**Result**: Essential constraints immediately visible, human-readable, Claude-loadable.

