## Achievement Summary

### Warnings Eliminated:  100%
- **Before**: 58 PytestUnknownMarkWarning (7 unregistered markers)
- **After**: 0 warnings ‚úÖ
- **Scope**: Test infrastructure (markers used across multiple test files)

### Zero Test Debt:  Maintained
