**Files Modified**:  1
- `pytest.ini` (7 lines added ‚Äî marker registrations)

**Total Lines Changed**: 7 (additions only) ‚úÖ

**Risk**:  Minimal
- Configuration-only change
- No code modifications
- No test logic changes
- Backward compatible
- Markers are metadata only
- Enhances functionality (enables filtering)

