## **Why This Three-Layer Approach Works**

| Layer | Purpose | Benefit |
|-------|---------|---------|
| **PR Comment** | Immediate feedback | Agent knows why rejected |
| **Bootstrap Learning** | Institutional memory | Future reference, searchable |
| **Governance Policy** | Enforcement | Prevents recurrence, enforceable |

**Without all three layers**:  Pattern repeats, you fight same battle again.

**With all three layers**: Pattern documented, policy enforced, precedent set.

