## Precedent:  PR #504 Case Study

**Status Claimed**:
- \"COMPLETE\"
- \"Only documentation nits\"
- \"Non-blocking failures\"

**Actual Status**:
- 92% pass rate (7 tests failing)
- 8% failure rate
- Test infrastructure incomplete

**CS2 Decision**:  REJECTED
\u003e \"If I allow 0.00001% to slip through it's going to catch up with me.  'Only' is not acceptable to me ‚Äî this is test dodging. \"

**Outcome**: Policy created, pattern documented, never again. 

