## Lessons Learned

**What Worked**:
1. Automated script for bulk replacements
2. Mechanical transformation (simple pattern)
3. Comprehensive inventory (COMPLETE_WARNING_INVENTORY.md)
4. Sequential verification (caught issues early)

**What Didn't Work** (Original Planning):
1. Deferred work = incomplete work
2. Speed vs. thoroughness (skipped inventory to meet timeline)
3. Assumption validation (assumed 365 baseline was complete)
4. Self-certification (no external review caught gaps)
5. Promises without evidence (builders confirmed without counts)

