- [ ] FM runs:  `pytest tests/ --tb=no -W all` daily
- [ ] Warning count = 0 (no regressions)
- [ ] Test debt patterns = 0 (no skips, TODOs, FIXMEs)

#### 4. **Escalation Discipline**
- [ ] API Builder escalates immediately on ambiguity/blocker
- [ ] FM responds within 4 hours (acknowledgment)
- [ ] FM resolves within 24 hours (or provides timeline)
- [ ] No "work around" behavior without escalation

