1. Detected the numbering conflict
2. Maintained canonical sequence integrity
3. Documented the reconciliation
4. Updated the FM repo reference (BOOTSTRAP-TEST-DODGING-001.md now says "BL-022")

**This is exactly how canonical governance should work** ‚Äî the source of truth maintains sequence, downstream repos adapt. 

