**Completion Report** (lines 116-154) documents: 
- ‚úÖ Correctness verification
- ‚úÖ Test alignment
- ‚úÖ Architecture adherence
- ‚úÖ Defect check
- ‚úÖ Tenant isolation

‚úÖ **CODE CHECKING REQUIREMENT MET**

