**Issue #429 Required**:
> "Checkpoint Required: At 50% (7 QA complete)"

**Assessment**: ‚ö†Ô∏è **NOT REPORTED AT 50%**

Builder completed all 15 QA in one cycle, so never reported at 50%.  This violates the checkpoint requirement (which is meant to catch issues early).

**Recommendation**: **MINOR VIOLATION** ‚Äî Builder should have paused at 7 QA to report, even if ready to continue.

