- ‚úÖ EH-2. 6-001:  Advanced Trend Forecasting (feature)
- ‚úÖ EH-2.6-002: Machine Learning Model Integration (feature)
- ‚úÖ EH-2.6-003: Advanced Report Export Formats (feature)

