- ‚úÖ Created #904 (governance repo): Mandate process improvement reflection
- ‚úÖ Created #518 (FM app repo): Layer down requirement after canonical policy established
- ‚è∏Ô∏è Bootstrap Learning will be registered after governance issue is resolved

