- ‚è∏Ô∏è FM MUST NOT mark any future builder work as COMPLETE without process improvement reflection
- ‚è∏Ô∏è FM MUST REJECT submissions that say "None identified" without justification for each question
- ‚è∏Ô∏è FM MUST escalate to me (CS2) if builders refuse to provide process improvements

